{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":944,"text":"So, people want a lot of things out of life,"},{"time":3566,"text":"but I think, more than anything else, they want happiness."},{"time":7461,"text":"Aristotle called happiness \"the chief good,\" the end"},{"time":10789,"text":"towards which all other things aim."},{"time":14061,"text":"According to this view, the reason we want a big house"},{"time":19581,"text":"or a nice car"},{"time":22214,"text":"or a good job"},{"time":24294,"text":"isn't that these things are intrinsically valuable."},{"time":26742,"text":"It's that we expect them to bring us"},{"time":29260,"text":"happiness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":30717,"text":"Now in the last 50 years, we Americans have gotten"},{"time":33349,"text":"a lot of the things that we want. We're richer."},{"time":35376,"text":"We live longer. We have access to technology"},{"time":38453,"text":"that would have seemed like science fiction"},{"time":40620,"text":"just a few years ago."},{"time":42861,"text":"The paradox of happiness is that even though the"},{"time":45285,"text":"objective conditions of our lives have improved dramatically,"},{"time":48187,"text":"we haven't actually gotten any happier."}]},{"cues":[{"time":51751,"text":"Maybe because these conventional notions of progress"},{"time":54670,"text":"haven't delivered big benefits in terms of happiness,"},{"time":57146,"text":"there's been an increased interest in recent years"},{"time":59276,"text":"in happiness itself."},{"time":61798,"text":"People have been debating the causes of happiness"},{"time":63833,"text":"for a really long time, in fact for thousands of years,"},{"time":66432,"text":"but it seems like many of those debates remain unresolved."},{"time":69889,"text":"Well, as with many other domains in life, I think"},{"time":71948,"text":"the scientific method has the potential to answer this question."},{"time":75160,"text":"In fact, in the last few years, there's been an explosion"},{"time":77694,"text":"in research on happiness. For example, we've learned a lot"},{"time":80495,"text":"about its demographics, how things like income"},{"time":83607,"text":"and education, gender and marriage relate to it."},{"time":87033,"text":"But one of the puzzles this has revealed is that"},{"time":89255,"text":"factors like these don't seem to have a particularly strong effect."},{"time":92194,"text":"Yes, it's better to make more money rather than less,"},{"time":94631,"text":"or to graduate from college instead of dropping out,"},{"time":97343,"text":"but the differences in happiness tend to be small."}]},{"cues":[{"time":100104,"text":"Which leaves the question, what are the big causes of happiness?"},{"time":103939,"text":"I think that's a question we haven't really answered yet,"},{"time":106636,"text":"but I think something that has the potential to be an answer"},{"time":109348,"text":"is that maybe happiness has an awful lot to do with"},{"time":112069,"text":"the contents of our moment-to-moment experiences."},{"time":114513,"text":"It certainly seems that we're going about our lives,"},{"time":116508,"text":"that what we're doing, who we're with, what we're thinking about,"},{"time":120443,"text":"have a big influence on our happiness, and yet"},{"time":122795,"text":"these are the very factors that have been very difficult,"},{"time":125028,"text":"in fact almost impossible, for scientists to study."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127415,"text":"A few years ago, I came up with a way to study people's happiness"},{"time":130476,"text":"moment to moment as they're going about their daily lives"},{"time":133055,"text":"on a massive scale all over the world, something we'd never"},{"time":135797,"text":"been able to do before. Called trackyourhappiness.org,"},{"time":138588,"text":"it uses the iPhone to monitor people's happiness in real time."},{"time":142874,"text":"How does this work? Basically, I send people signals"},{"time":145663,"text":"at random points throughout the day, and then I ask them"},{"time":148103,"text":"a bunch of questions about their moment-to-moment experience"},{"time":150391,"text":"at the instant just before the signal."},{"time":152925,"text":"The idea is that, if we can watch how people's happiness"},{"time":155732,"text":"goes up and down over the course of the day,"},{"time":158356,"text":"minute to minute in some cases,"},{"time":160084,"text":"and try to understand how what people are doing,"},{"time":162226,"text":"who they're with, what they're thinking about, and all"},{"time":165069,"text":"the other factors that describe our day, how those might"},{"time":167245,"text":"relate to those changes in happiness, we might be able"},{"time":169956,"text":"to discover some of the things that really have"},{"time":171502,"text":"a big influence on happiness."},{"time":173807,"text":"We've been fortunate with this project to collect"},{"time":176113,"text":"quite a lot of data, a lot more data of this kind than I think"},{"time":178971,"text":"has ever been collected before,"},{"time":180830,"text":"over 650,000 real-time reports"},{"time":184051,"text":"from over 15,000 people."},{"time":186930,"text":"And it's not just a lot of people, it's a really diverse group,"},{"time":190039,"text":"people from a wide range of ages, from 18 to late 80s,"},{"time":193526,"text":"a wide range of incomes, education levels,"},{"time":196454,"text":"people who are married, divorced, widowed, etc."},{"time":199517,"text":"They collectively represent every one of"},{"time":201781,"text":"86 occupational categories and hail from over 80 countries."}]},{"cues":[{"time":206642,"text":"What I'd like to do with the rest of my time with you today"},{"time":209544,"text":"is talk a little bit about one of the areas that we've been"},{"time":211673,"text":"investigating, and that's mind-wandering."},{"time":214856,"text":"As human beings, we have this unique ability"},{"time":217256,"text":"to have our minds stray away from the present."},{"time":220191,"text":"This guy is sitting here working on his computer,"},{"time":222116,"text":"and yet he could be thinking about"},{"time":223170,"text":"the vacation he had last month,"},{"time":225859,"text":"wondering what he's going to have for dinner."},{"time":227822,"text":"Maybe he's worried that he's going bald. (Laughter)"},{"time":231655,"text":"This ability to focus our attention on something other"},{"time":234440,"text":"than the present is really amazing. It allows us to learn"},{"time":237695,"text":"and plan and reason in ways that no other species of animal can."},{"time":242189,"text":"And yet it's not clear what the relationship is"},{"time":244587,"text":"between our use of this ability and our happiness."},{"time":248503,"text":"You've probably heard people suggest that you should"},{"time":250361,"text":"stay focused on the present. \"Be here now,\""},{"time":252852,"text":"you've probably heard a hundred times."},{"time":254337,"text":"Maybe, to really be happy, we need to stay completely"},{"time":257018,"text":"immersed and focused on our experience in the moment."},{"time":260529,"text":"Maybe these people are right. Maybe mind-wandering"},{"time":262363,"text":"is a bad thing."},{"time":264093,"text":"On the other hand, when our minds wander,"},{"time":266512,"text":"they're unconstrained. We can't change the physical reality"},{"time":269173,"text":"in front of us, but we can go anywhere in our minds."},{"time":272561,"text":"Since we know people want to be happy, maybe"},{"time":274374,"text":"when our minds wander, they're going to someplace happier than the place"},{"time":277065,"text":"that they're leaving. It would make a lot of sense."},{"time":279298,"text":"In other words, maybe the pleasures of the mind"},{"time":280796,"text":"allow us to increase our happiness with mind-wandering."}]},{"cues":[{"time":285222,"text":"Well, since I'm a scientist, I'd like to try to"},{"time":287233,"text":"resolve this debate with some data, and in particular"},{"time":289910,"text":"I'd like to present some data to you from three questions"},{"time":292398,"text":"that I ask with Track Your Happiness. Remember, this is from"},{"time":294608,"text":"sort of moment-to-moment experience in people's real lives."},{"time":297260,"text":"There are three questions. The first one is a happiness question:"},{"time":300290,"text":"How do you feel, on a scale ranging from very bad"},{"time":303165,"text":"to very good? Second, an activity question:"},{"time":307304,"text":"What are you doing, on a list of 22 different activities"},{"time":309832,"text":"including things like eating and working and watching TV?"},{"time":313057,"text":"And finally a mind-wandering question:"},{"time":316645,"text":"Are you thinking about something other"},{"time":319287,"text":"than what you're currently doing?"},{"time":321910,"text":"People could say no -- in other words, I'm focused only on my task --"},{"time":325352,"text":"or yes -- I am thinking about something else --"},{"time":327881,"text":"and the topic of those thoughts are pleasant,"},{"time":330337,"text":"neutral or unpleasant."},{"time":331763,"text":"Any of those yes responses are what we called mind-wandering."}]},{"cues":[{"time":337222,"text":"So what did we find?"},{"time":339687,"text":"This graph shows happiness on the vertical axis,"},{"time":341986,"text":"and you can see that bar there representing how happy"},{"time":344226,"text":"people are when they're focused on the present,"},{"time":345559,"text":"when they're not mind-wandering."},{"time":347482,"text":"As it turns out, people are substantially less happy"},{"time":351201,"text":"when their minds are wandering than when they're not."},{"time":355937,"text":"Now you might look at this result and say, okay, sure,"},{"time":358539,"text":"on average people are less happy when they're mind-wandering,"},{"time":360961,"text":"but surely when their minds are straying away"},{"time":362629,"text":"from something that wasn't very enjoyable to begin with,"},{"time":364748,"text":"at least then mind-wandering should be doing something good for us."},{"time":368512,"text":"Nope. As it turns out,"},{"time":371211,"text":"people are less happy when they're mind-wandering"},{"time":372903,"text":"no matter what they're doing. For example,"},{"time":375929,"text":"people don't really like commuting to work very much."},{"time":378106,"text":"It's one of their least enjoyable activities, and yet"},{"time":380866,"text":"they are substantially happier when they're focused"},{"time":383400,"text":"only on their commute than when their mind is going"},{"time":385762,"text":"off to something else."},{"time":388809,"text":"It's amazing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":390591,"text":"So how could this be happening? I think part of the reason,"},{"time":394436,"text":"a big part of the reason, is that when our minds wander,"},{"time":396834,"text":"we often think about unpleasant things, and they are"},{"time":399690,"text":"enormously less happy when they do that,"},{"time":403297,"text":"our worries, our anxieties, our regrets,"},{"time":405962,"text":"and yet even when people are thinking about something"},{"time":408922,"text":"neutral, they're still considerably less happy"},{"time":411786,"text":"than when they're not mind-wandering at all."},{"time":413763,"text":"Even when they're thinking about something they would describe as pleasant,"},{"time":416598,"text":"they're actually just slightly less happy"},{"time":418802,"text":"than when they aren't mind-wandering."},{"time":422059,"text":"If mind-wandering were a slot machine, it would be like"},{"time":424121,"text":"having the chance to lose 50 dollars, 20 dollars"},{"time":427154,"text":"or one dollar. Right? You'd never want to play. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":433305,"text":"So I've been talking about this, suggesting, perhaps,"},{"time":435978,"text":"that mind-wandering causes unhappiness, but all"},{"time":438790,"text":"I've really shown you is that these two things are correlated."},{"time":441557,"text":"It's possible that's the case, but it might also be the case"},{"time":444342,"text":"that when people are unhappy, then they mind-wander."},{"time":446796,"text":"Maybe that's what's really going on. How could we ever"},{"time":449165,"text":"disentangle these two possibilites?"},{"time":452254,"text":"Well, one fact that we can take advantage of, I think a fact"},{"time":454598,"text":"you'll all agree is true, is that time goes forward, not"},{"time":457555,"text":"backward. Right? The cause has to come before the effect."},{"time":461552,"text":"We're lucky in this data we have many responses from each person,"},{"time":464982,"text":"and so we can look and see, does mind-wandering"},{"time":468178,"text":"tend to precede unhappiness, or does unhappiness"},{"time":470671,"text":"tend to precede mind-wandering, to get some insight"},{"time":472854,"text":"into the causal direction."},{"time":475015,"text":"As it turns out, there is a strong relationship between"},{"time":478224,"text":"mind-wandering now and being unhappy a short time later,"},{"time":481909,"text":"consistent with the idea that mind-wandering is causing people to be unhappy."},{"time":485628,"text":"In contrast, there's no relationship between being unhappy"},{"time":488788,"text":"now and mind-wandering a short time later."},{"time":491797,"text":"In other words, mind-wandering very likely seems to be"},{"time":494119,"text":"an actual cause, and not merely a consequence, of unhappiness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":499959,"text":"A few minutes ago, I likened mind-wandering"},{"time":502183,"text":"to a slot machine you'd never want to play."},{"time":504446,"text":"Well, how often do people's minds wander?"},{"time":506750,"text":"Turns out, they wander a lot. In fact, really a lot."},{"time":511207,"text":"Forty-seven percent of the time, people are thinking"},{"time":513901,"text":"about something other than what they're currently doing."},{"time":517308,"text":"How does that depend on what people are doing?"},{"time":519746,"text":"This shows the rate of mind-wandering across 22 activities"},{"time":522499,"text":"ranging from a high of 65 percent — (Laughter) —"},{"time":526498,"text":"when people are taking a shower, brushing their teeth,"},{"time":529010,"text":"to 50 percent when they're working,"},{"time":531911,"text":"to 40 percent when they're exercising,"},{"time":534954,"text":"all the way down to this one short bar on the right"},{"time":536873,"text":"that I think some of you are probably laughing at."},{"time":538861,"text":"Ten percent of the time people's minds are wandering"},{"time":541251,"text":"when they're having sex. (Laughter)"},{"time":545822,"text":"But there's something I think that's quite interesting in this graph,"},{"time":548755,"text":"and that is, basically with one exception,"},{"time":551803,"text":"no matter what people are doing, they're mind-wandering"},{"time":553981,"text":"at least 30 percent of the time, which suggests, I think,"},{"time":557659,"text":"that mind-wandering isn't just frequent, it's ubiquitous."},{"time":560490,"text":"It pervades basically everything that we do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":564223,"text":"In my talk today, I've told you a little bit about mind-wandering,"},{"time":567419,"text":"a variable that I think turns out to be fairly important"},{"time":569469,"text":"in the equation for happiness."},{"time":571125,"text":"My hope is that over time, by tracking people's"},{"time":573140,"text":"moment-to-moment happiness and their experiences"},{"time":576188,"text":"in daily life, we'll be able to uncover a lot of important causes of happiness,"},{"time":579590,"text":"and then in the end, a scientific understanding of happiness"},{"time":582520,"text":"will help us create a future that's not only richer"},{"time":585217,"text":"and healthier, but happier as well."},{"time":588079,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"},{"time":591303,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}